Class FlexibleFeature

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Feature, Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable

    public class FlexibleFeature
extends BasicFeature
    a FlexibleFeature based on BasicFeature originally used by the GeoJSON reader. currently adding - "autoextends" by returning null for undefined attribs - lazy conversion of attributes (see getAttribute(int)) currently String, Date, Time, Timestamp
